SASS Notes

MAP
ex: 
$font-weights: (
  "regular": 400,
  "medium": 500,
  "bold": 700
);

body {
  font-weight: map-get($font-weights, bold);
  }
  
mag aapply sa css yung value na nakalagay sa sass

magiging font-weight: 700 sya


NESTING
example
.main {
  width: 80%;
  margin: 0 auto;
    
    p {
      font-weight: map-get($font-weights, bold);
    }
}
magiging ganto sa css
.main p {
  font-weight: 700;
}


AMPERSAND
.parent {
  .child {}
}
then it can be 
.parent {
  & .child {}
}

INTERPOLATION
to be continued..
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_a5j7KoflTs&list=PLLah4xHYIASBG7GCKZa12md4exHNf2kQY&index=12
https://sass-lang.com/documentation/interpolation#:~:text=Interpolation%20can%20be%20used%20almost,Property%20names%20in%20declarations

PARTIALS
-A Sass file lead by underscore
-not generate a CSS file.
-compiler ignore those file
example: 
_resets.scss
main.scss
  @import './resets';  
-they did not include the _

FUNCTION
-works like javascript

MIXINS
@mixin flexCenter {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

.main {
  @include flexCenter;
}

PASS AN ARGUMENT TO MIXIN


